{"tid":2508110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奧斯卡創收視新低 Trump:「搞政治正確又無聊」","createTime":"2021-04-28T13:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T14:20:09.000Z","uid":75656,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6a168d6006e81cd7d46afe1f3c43541bd526ed5e","tid":2508110,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:12:23.000Z","msg":"第93屆奧斯卡昨順利落幕，美中不足的是收視率創下史上新低，這讓向來與美演藝界關係不睦的前總統川普大肆嘲諷，建議奧斯卡應該改變典禮進行的方式和內容。<br />\n<br />\n川普辦公室針對本屆奧斯卡獎發出聲明，寫道「奧斯卡創下史上最低收視率，甚至比去年還低，如果他們持續用目前這種可笑的方式進行典禮，情況只會變得更糟。」<br />\n<br />\n川普認為，奧斯卡應該把名稱改回「演藝學院獎」，且「不要那麼政治正確和無聊，把事情做好。還有，把主持人找回來，這些藝人花時間思考怎麼吹捧民主黨，是在摧毀我們的國家，還封殺了保守、共和黨人，這種模式著實是運作不良。」<br />\n<br />\n川普去年也曾公開批評奧斯卡說，「不敢相信南韓電影《寄生上流》獲最佳影片，到底搞什麼鬼？」、「起先我還以為他只能拿到最佳外語片呢。」<br />\n<br />\n根據AGB尼爾森公布收視調查，本屆奧斯卡頒獎典禮收視人口跌破千萬大關，僅吸引985萬收視人口，較去年銳減58%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3513716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3513716&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=c4e42e58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3513716&h=5b84472a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3513716</a>"},{"pid":"76228cb7d79afa3b29ceac58d4ea75aa2caeaa5d","tid":2508110,"uid":308567,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"美國老衲"},{"pid":"8a9137dbcdbb3b5dc9350f49e18410ec4b9e4b97","tid":2508110,"uid":30384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d9dff4d720acce75e23af1de7554a